<p class="Note"><sup>a</sup>For Lyme disease suspected during pregnancy, use appropriate antibiotics for stage of pregnancy. <br/>
<sup>b</sup>Do not use azithromycin to treat people with cardiac abnormalities associated with Lyme disease because of its effect on QT interval.</p>
