<p>In addition, a NICE pathway titled "Lyme disease overview" is provided on the <a href="/web/20180712182957/https://www.guideline.gov/Home/Disclaimer?id=51324&amp;contentType=summary&amp;redirect=https%3a%2f%2fpathways.nice.org.uk%2fpathways%2flyme-disease" title="NICE Web site">NICE Web site</a>&nbsp;<img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180712182957im_/https://www.guideline.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif"/>.</p></div></p>

